node.title: vTuber Kit
node.description: VTuber kit is an all-in-one solution for those getting started with VTubing. Users can customize colors, mix-and-match clothes, pick out various hair parts, and slap on accessories to create something they like.

node.description: An overlay that allows Twitch streamers to have an interactive audience that performs wotagei. User can customize when and how animations are triggers, and they can replace the audience members, lightsticks, and bits burst with their own images.
